snippet.title: City 20 - Consequences
snippet.description:
City 20 is a sandbox survival game coming to early access on PC in 2024. 
In this video one of our team members describes some of the consequences the behavior of the player can have on NPCs and factions.

Whislist it on Steam https://store.steampowered.com/app/1597980?utm_source=consequences

Whislist it on EGS https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/city-20-32eb30
